Ousmane Diabaté (ka amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 9 n'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 1994) bụ onye Nigerien na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbara Al-Minaa na ndị otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Niger bọọlụ.
Na 23 Jenụwarị 2022, Diabaté sonyeere klọb Al-Minaa nke Iraq site na klọb Muaither nke Qatar.
Diabaté mere egwuregwu izizi ya maka otu egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Niger na egwuregwu enyi na enyi 3-3 na Central African Republic na 27 Mee 2018.
